# WanHammer
First Game with XCODE Swift - Project 3 - OpenClassRoom's

Welcome to the WanHammer Game :

Games Rules : 


First step : 
Choose Your :
- Team Name
- User Name
- 4 Fighters (Human, dwarf, magician, Colossus)
- Favorite Number beetween 1 and 10


Second Step : 
The Battle !
- You can check life point of each fighters
- You can check the last action
- Sometimes, you can choose a new weapon at the beginning of the round/or you can eat a bigMac/ or a Fruit
- You have to choose which fighter do an action
- You have to choose which opponent on the action will be done
BONUS ZONE : 
- If you're lucky, you can use your special attack
- If you're lucky ++  you can use a critical attack 
- If you're really bad, your CRITICAL ATTACK is missed, and your attack is not on the opponent but on one of your fighter


If your fighter's life point fall to 0 : he's dead 

Third Step : When 3 fighter's of one team are dead : 
- Congrats announcement 
- Showing the count of round



SORRY FOR MY ENGLISH ;). I'm begginer 

COLLABORATE : 
- I'm student, so I have to practice and build this game alone
- You can fork this project
- Create a new branch "Develop" + "Nickname"
- Be clear on your Commit
- Give me a pull request 

Enjoy ;) 
